]]}},{"name":"70:30","price":"kecuali terhadap istri-istri mereka atau hamba sahaya yang mereka miliki865) maka sesungguhnya mereka tidak tercela.","arabic":"إِلَّا عَلَىٰٓ أَزۡوَٰجِهِمۡ أَوۡ مَا مَلَكَتۡ أَيۡمَٰنُهُمۡ فَإِنَّهُمۡ غَيۡرُ مَلُومِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5405,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"*865) Hamba sahaya yang didapat dalam peperangan dengan orang kafir. Dalam peperangan dengan orang-orang kafir itu, perempuan-perempuan yang ditawan biasanya dibagi-bagikan kepada kaum muslimin yang ikut dalam peperangan, dan kebiasaan ini bukanlah sesuatu yang diwajibkan.","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"illā ʿalā azwājihim aw mā malakat aymānuhum fa-innahum ghayru malūmīna ","translations":["Except","from","their spouses","or","what","they possess","rightfully","then indeed, they","(are) not","blameworthy","(30)"],"transliterationArr":["illā","ʿalā","azwājihim","aw","mā","malakat","aymānuhum","fa-innahum","ghayru","malūmīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,800],[2,800,2980],[3,2980,4420],[4,4420,4790],[5,4790,5170],[6,5170,5970],[7,5970,7340],[8,7340,9170],[9,9170,9750],[10,9750,12705]]}},{"name":"70:31","price":"Maka barangsiapa mencari di luar itu (seperti zina, homoseks, dan lesbian), mereka itulah orang-orang yang melampaui batas.","arabic":"فَمَنِ ٱبۡتَغَىٰ وَرَآءَ ذَٰلِكَ فَأُوْلَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلۡعَادُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5406,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"famani ib'taghā warāa dhālika fa-ulāika humu al-ʿādūna ","translations":["But whoever","seeks","beyond","that","then those","[they]","(are) the transgressors ","(31)"],"transliterationArr":["famani","ib'taghā","warāa","dhālika","fa-ulāika","humu","al-ʿādūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1440],[3,1440,3500],[4,3500,4240],[5,4240,6759],[6,6759,7099],[7,7099,10094]]}},{"name":"70:32","price":"Dan orang-orang yang memelihara amanat dan janjinya,","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ لِأَمَٰنَٰتِهِمۡ وَعَهۡدِهِمۡ رَٰعُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5407,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna hum li-amānātihim waʿahdihim rāʿūna ","translations":["And those who","[they]","of their trusts","and their promise","(are) observers","(32)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","hum","li-amānātihim","waʿahdihim","rāʿūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1230],[2,1230,1540],[3,1540,3340],[4,3340,4420],[5,4420,7235]]}},{"name":"70:33","price":"dan orang-orang yang berpegang teguh pada kesaksiannya,","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُم بِشَهَٰدَٰتِهِمۡ قَآئِمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5408,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna hum bishahādātihim qāimūna ","translations":["And those who","[they]","in their testimonies","stand firm","(33)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","hum","bishahādātihim","qāimūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,2060],[3,2060,3940],[4,3940,8905]]}},{"name":"70:34","price":"dan orang-orang yang memelihara salatnya.","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَلَىٰ صَلَاتِهِمۡ يُحَافِظُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5409,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna hum ʿalā ṣalātihim yuḥāfiẓūna ","translations":["And those who","[they]","on","their prayer","keep a guard ","(34)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","hum","ʿalā","ṣalātihim","yuḥāfiẓūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1230],[2,1230,1600],[3,1600,2180],[4,2180,3350],[5,3350,7065]]}},{"name":"70:35","price":"Mereka itu dimuliakan di dalam surga.","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ فِي جَنَّٰتٖ مُّكۡرَمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5410,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"ulāika fī jannātin muk'ramūna ","translations":["Those","(will be) in","Gardens","honored","(35)"],"transliterationArr":["ulāika","fī","jannātin","muk'ramūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2530],[2,2530,2900],[3,2900,4920],[4,4920,8705]]}},{"name":"70:36","price":"Maka mengapa orang-orang kafir itu datang bergegas ke hadapanmu (Muhammad),","arabic":"فَمَالِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ قِبَلَكَ مُهۡطِعِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5411,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"famāli alladhīna kafarū qibalaka muh'ṭiʿīna ","translations":["So what is with","those who","disbelieve","before you","(they) hasten","(36)"],"transliterationArr":["famāli","alladhīna","kafarū","qibalaka","muh'ṭiʿīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,790],[2,790,1700],[3,1700,2520],[4,2520,3390],[5,3390,6335]]}},{"name":"70:37","price":"dari kanan dan dari kiri dengan berkelompok-kelompok?866)","arabic":"عَنِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ وَعَنِ ٱلشِّمَالِ عِزِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5412,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"*866) Menurut keterangan sebagian mufasir ayat ini berhubungan dengan peristiwa ketika Rasulullah salat dan membaca Al-Qur`an di dekat Ka'bah lalu orang-orang musyrik berkumpul berkelompok-kelompok di hadapannya sambil mengejek dan mengatakan, \"Jika orang-orang mukmin benar-benar akan masuk surga sebagaimana kata Muhammad kitalah yang akan masuk terlebih dahulu.\" Maka turunlah ayat 38.","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿani al-yamīni waʿani al-shimāli ʿizīna ","translations":["On","the right","and on","the left","(in) separate groups","(37)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿani","al-yamīni","waʿani","al-shimāli","ʿizīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,1420],[3,1420,1990],[4,1990,2950],[5,2950,5635]]}},{"name":"70:38","price":"Apakah setiap orang dari orang-orang kafir itu ingin masuk surga yang penuh kenikmatan?","arabic":"أَيَطۡمَعُ كُلُّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ أَن يُدۡخَلَ جَنَّةَ نَعِيمٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5413,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"ayaṭmaʿu kullu im'ri-in min'hum an yud'khala jannata naʿīmin ","translations":["Does long","every","person","among them","that","he enters","a Garden","(of) Delight","(38)"],"transliterationArr":["ayaṭmaʿu","kullu","im'ri-in","min'hum","an","yud'khala","jannata","naʿīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1040],[2,1040,1600],[3,1600,2250],[4,2250,3800],[5,3800,5730],[6,5730,7380],[7,7380,10085]]}},{"name":"70:39","price":"tidak mungkin! Sesungguhnya Kami menciptakan mereka dari apa yang mereka ketahui.867)","arabic":"كَلَّآۖ إِنَّا خَلَقۡنَٰهُم مِّمَّا يَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5414,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"*867) Bahwa mereka orang-orang kafir diciptakan Allah dari air mani untuk beriman dan bertakwa kepada-Nya, sebagaimana yang disampaikan oleh Rasul. Jadi kalau mereka tidak beriman tidak berhak masuk surga.","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā innā khalaqnāhum mimmā yaʿlamūna ","translations":["By no means","Indeed, We","[We] have created them","from what","they know","(39)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","innā","khalaqnāhum","mimmā","yaʿlamūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,970],[2,970,3170],[3,3170,4490],[4,4490,6550],[5,6550,9785]]}},{"name":"70:40","price":"Maka Aku bersumpah demi Tuhan yang mengatur tempat-tempat terbit dan terbenamnya (matahari, bulan dan bintang), sungguh, Kami pasti mampu,","arabic":"فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِرَبِّ ٱلۡمَشَٰرِقِ وَٱلۡمَغَٰرِبِ إِنَّا لَقَٰدِرُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5415,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"falā uq'simu birabbi al-mashāriqi wal-maghāribi innā laqādirūna ","translations":["But nay","I swear","by (the) Lord","(of) the risings","and the settings","that We","(are) surely Able","(40)"],"transliterationArr":["falā","uq'simu","birabbi","al-mashāriqi","wal-maghāribi","innā","laqādirūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1860],[2,1860,2690],[3,2690,3440],[4,3440,4650],[5,4650,5970],[6,5970,7440],[7,7440,10645]]}},{"name":"70:41","price":"untuk mengganti (mereka) dengan kaum yang lebih baik dari mereka, dan Kami tidak dapat dikalahkan.","arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّبَدِّلَ خَيۡرٗا مِّنۡهُمۡ وَمَا نَحۡنُ بِمَسۡبُوقِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5416,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿalā an nubaddila khayran min'hum wamā naḥnu bimasbūqīna ","translations":["[On]","to","[We] replace","(with) better","than them","and not","We","(are) to be outrun","(41)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿalā","an","nubaddila","khayran","min'hum","wamā","naḥnu","bimasbūqīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1960],[2,1960,2310],[3,2310,3890],[4,3890,4530],[5,4530,6210],[6,6210,6760],[7,6760,7370],[8,7370,10855]]}},{"name":"70:42","price":"Maka biarkanlah mereka tenggelam dan bermain-main (dalam kesesatan) sampai mereka menjumpai hari yang diancamkan kepada mereka,","arabic":"فَذَرۡهُمۡ يَخُوضُواْ وَيَلۡعَبُواْ حَتَّىٰ يُلَٰقُواْ يَوۡمَهُمُ ٱلَّذِي يُوعَدُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5417,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"fadharhum yakhūḍū wayalʿabū ḥattā yulāqū yawmahumu alladhī yūʿadūna ","translations":["So leave them","(to) converse vainly","and amuse themselves","until","they meet","their Day","which","they are promised","(42)"],"transliterationArr":["fadharhum","yakhūḍū","wayalʿabū","ḥattā","yulāqū","yawmahumu","alladhī","yūʿadūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,2130],[3,2130,3210],[4,3210,4030],[5,4030,5020],[6,5020,6070],[7,6070,6950],[8,6950,10115]]}},{"name":"70:43","price":"(yaitu) pada hari ketika mereka keluar dari kubur dengan cepat seakan-akan mereka pergi dengan segera kepada berhala-berhala (sewaktu di dunia),","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَخۡرُجُونَ مِنَ ٱلۡأَجۡدَاثِ سِرَاعٗا كَأَنَّهُمۡ إِلَىٰ نُصُبٖ ي